All paths are relative

New solution
dotnet new sln -o SolutionName

New Project (without cd, creates subfolder for project)
dotnet new short-name -o ProjectName

Add project to solution
dotnet sln SolutionName.sln add path/to/project.csproj

Add project reference
dotnet add path/to/project.csproj reference path/to/project.csproj

Build project (maybe)
dotnet build

Run project
dotnet run [in project directory]
dotnet path/to/bin/Debug/net8.0/project.dll
